dkDLCcLTpFT7k3ZzmYg">Ngải Tính Phu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chung-Tinh/Giang-h%C3%A0nh-b%C3%A0i-th%E1%BB%83-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-UlNUhlN33BbE5zXYPpqudQ">Giang hành bài thể kỳ 1 - 江行俳體其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chung-Tinh/author-u6-RIhUvEY9JL42vswhrag">Chung Tinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/H%E1%BA%A1nh-li%C3%AAm-t%E1%BA%A1i-v%E1%BB%8Dng/poem-LgHeBllv63cr3B-blNsABQ">Hạnh liêm tại vọng - 杏帘在望</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Duy-T%C3%B9ng/Nh%E1%BB%8B-nh%E1%BA%ADt-tuy%E1%BA%BFt-b%E1%BA%A5t-ch%E1%BB%89/poem-QORdWKuyajaBEabKxpfdVw">Nhị nhật tuyết bất chỉ - 二日雪不止</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Duy-T%C3%B9ng/author-cG-6f2ETrxSYJLcjUNmVzg">Trần Duy Tùng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-C%E1%BB%B1-c%C3%A1c/poem-MfKpwVwDcfosrtLRicYxaA">Thạch Cự các - 石柜閣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
